**P0 scope:** The dedicated tap-target capture `8_taptargets.png` was **missing** (no `.mp4`, no frames), so I resolved the two P0 tap-target items directly from iOS source. The other P0 clip `4.3_txn_form_types` was present and confirmed pickers-in-context.

